{"tid":1710924,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"開花定入中大","createTime":"2019-11-12T09:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T10:17:13.000Z","uid":216008,"like":55,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"9f20f4ca9bc6cea7c71925ff284df1049aef046d","tid":1710924,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:12:53.000Z","msg":"考慮因素在於開花會做啲乜<br />\n如果各區開花：<br />\n- 無火魔，無警署，無政府部門<br />\n- 齋RB，齋口號<br />\n班狗睬你有味<br />\n<strong>當然我都唔係叫你火魔，警署，政府部門啦</strong><br />\n<br />\n如果反包中大：<br />\n- 交通問題<br />\n- 裝備點樣安全收埋<br />\n- 有幾多人會跟隊入中大<br />\n<br />\n呢個係基於理性既諗法，唔係話要開花就開花，要反包就反包，大家請自行思考<br />\n今日一定要有行動，但絕對唔可以盲頭烏蠅"},{"pid":"f289466a5675861c21192d2953a76dfe785344dc","tid":1710924,"uid":316537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:13:52.000Z","msg":"both"},{"pid":"88ba6459159f3fef52618f57d9952c93a7ddf687","tid":1710924,"uid":216008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f289466a5675861c21192d2953a76dfe785344dc","tid":1710924,"uid":316537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:13:52.000Z","msg":"both"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:15:46.000Z","msg":"都可以，所以到最後就算一齊做都好，咁開花既活動要做啲乜，反包點樣先成功<br />\n當然前題係要人得人，如果要人無人既話暴大手足一定收皮"},{"pid":"b46e4939821261861c003f494ca6d3bc8d9acc8b","tid":1710924,"uid":30084,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:17:26.000Z","msg":"好聽就開花 唔好聽就鳩企<br />\n<br />\n你冇行動逼走佢 開條柒花咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夠閪譫燒狗屋"},{"pid":"8271b88bb0db632bacc11e992b454dbe9c6de3fe","tid":1710924,"uid":271475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:19:00.000Z","msg":"BOTH LA"},{"pid":"ea6fe053f318771b18cd8c548532a03fb66909b3","tid":1710924,"uid":147916,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T09:19:29.000Z","msg":"⚠轉出去⚠<br />\n❗大學 Lab 善用化學品反抗❗<br />\n❗HNO3❗<br />\n❗Mg❗<br />\n❗NH4NO3❗<br />\n❗NaOH❗<br />\n❗ANFO❗<br />\n❗ANSU❗"},{"pid":"55db89bc